<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.7.8">
<l>vārā kamatā kiyimmaṇ ṇaiyiṭantāy</l>
<l>nārā yaṇaṉē nallavē tiyarnāṅkūr</l>
<l>cīrār poḻilcūḻ tiruveḷ ḷakkuḷattuḷ</l>
<l>ārā vamutē yaṭiyēṟ karuḷāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, becoming Varāha, dug up this earth, Nārāyaṇa,</l>
<l>Never-sating nectar in Tiruveḷḷakkuḷam, encircled by fine groves,</l>
<l>In Nāṅkūr with good Vedic experts,</l>
<l>Be gracious to me, your servant.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
